+package common
+
+import "encoding/json"
+
+// Job 任务信息
+type Job struct {
+	Name    string `json:"name,omitempty"`     // 任务名称
+	Command string `json:"command,omitempty"`  // 命令
+	CronExp string `json:"cron_exp,omitempty"` // crontab 表达式
+}
+
+// 返回值
+type Response struct {
+	Status  int
+	ErrCode int
+	Data    interface{}
+}
+
+// 创建返回值
+func BuildReponse(Status int, ErrCode int, Data interface{}) (response []byte, err error) {
+	var (
+		resp Response
+	)
+
+	resp = Response{
+		Status:  Status,
+		ErrCode: ErrCode,
+		Data:    Data,
+	}
+
+	resposne, err = json.Marshal(resp)
+	return
+}
